#: src/mathlib.c:1033
#, c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"* Notice: \"%s\" was selected, but you can only change to a\n"
"* different Intel MKL threading library by restarting xnec2c.\n"
"* \n"
"* However, you may continue to select any other Linear Algebra library\n"
"* without restart, including this same Intel MKL library.  All other\n"
"* Intel MKL threading libraries are disabled until restart because of an \n"
"* MKL limitation where the MKL threading library can only be dynamically\n"
"* linked only once per runtime.\n"
"* \n"
"* See Intel's documentation on mkl_set_threading_layer() for more detail.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"* Pemberitahuan: \"%s\" dipilih, tetapi Anda hanya dapat beralih ke\n"
"* pustaka threading Intel MKL yang berbeda dengan memulai ulang xnec2c.\n"
"* \n"
"* Namun, Anda dapat terus memilih pustaka Aljabar Linear lainnya\n"
"* tanpa restart, termasuk pustaka Intel MKL yang sama ini. Semua pustaka\n"
"* threading Intel MKL lainnya dinonaktifkan hingga restart karena\n"
"* keterbatasan MKL di mana pustaka threading MKL hanya dapat ditautkan\n"
"* secara dinamis satu kali per runtime.\n"
"* \n"
"* Lihat dokumentasi Intel tentang mkl_set_threading_layer() untuk "
"detailnya.\n"

